        Create an object. オブジェクトを生成します
        Parameters:
        api - BlockStudioAPI
        name - Object's name.
        baseLocation - Spawn at this location.
        useBukkitArmorStand - Whether to use BukkitArmorStand. If you specify true for this argument, you will not be able to move the object asynchronously.
